Re: bitcoin 0.3 win64 - broken access to APPDATA if non-latin characters in
username

Bitcointalk

2010-07-09 15:37:05 UTC - [11]Original Post

   I tested this with a non-lower-ASCII account name on XP and confirmed
   the bug, then tested that the new GetDefaultDataDir fixed it.  This
   change is revision 102 of the SVN.
